author: dlr
msg: On the merge-tracking branch: Fix merge test #12, which was failing
due to notification of a merge into an svn:mergeinfo property
(reported as " G" by the command-line client) which is effectively a
no-op (a delta "- /A:1" into a path with no merge info).
To paraphrase Malcolm Rowe, "the notification is correct, since we
merged a change to that property.  However, the notification doesn't
guarantee that the property will have changed state after the fact."
notification from a no-op property merge.
